{"tid":1053455,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英外交副部長回應港府修訂引渡條文　聲稱香港立法不宜作評論？","createTime":"2019-03-09T05:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T06:59:33.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8962dee8e9e1801331c4b0624feda78c3276eeeb","tid":1053455,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/09/133604_1d4ca41d785445dddd1fb7254b8a2a04.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F09%2F133604_1d4ca41d785445dddd1fb7254b8a2a04.png&h=1b8cb7d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就著港府修訂引渡條文，素來關心香港議題的英國上議院議員奧爾頓勛爵（Lord Alton of Liverpool）早前撰寫了書面質詢，關注英國政府對修例取態及有否違反《中英聯合聲明》。<br />\n<br />\n想不到英國外交部副部長阿瑪德（Lord Ahmad of Wimbledon）竟回覆表示：「英國政府留意到香港政府計劃修訂引渡條例，公眾諮詢將於下月底結束，我們在立法過程不適宜作評論。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOZbVG2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOZbVG2.png&h=2a99b088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n實情是，香港保安局局長李家超早就明言拒絕進行諮詢，只在網站列明公眾可在不遲於三月四日提交意見，真的不能得知英國政府所謂「港府公眾諮詢至下月底」的說法從何而來，根本與事實不符。<br />\n<br />\n至於英國外交部副部長表示「立法過程不適宜作評論」更是難以理解，翻查資料早見英國政府在痛陳廿三條立法的弊處。既然官員當年可以直斥香港本地立法充斥魔鬼細節，只說明英國當局作為《中英聯合聲明》的簽署國，根本有位置與責任監察香港高度自治的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，既然本地商界、台灣政界及美國領事與商會相繼表達憂慮甚至反對，我亦希望英政府重拾當年看待廿三條立法的認真態度，審慎檢視引渡條文修訂的禍害，莫縱容港府通過這條可以引渡在港英國公民到中國受審的修例通過。<br />\n<br />\n作者 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/英外交副部長回應港府修訂引渡條文-聲稱香港立法不宜作評論/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E5%89%AF%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1%E6%A2%9D%E6%96%87-%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E4%BD%9C%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%2F&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6ufbhcgmijv%2F0DJBpEVBRbRs%3D&h=b2329bdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E5%89%AF%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1%E6%A2%9D%E6%96%87-%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E4%BD%9C%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%2F&h=30bff735\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/英外交副部長回應港府修訂引渡條文-聲稱香港立法不宜作評論/</a>"},{"pid":"95e63475bc51f4267f2a597080dc5482a4826254","tid":1053455,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:46:20.000Z","msg":"因為英國已經諗住放大大隻航空母艦喺南支那海<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/jul/21/south-china-sea-uk-could-send-aircraft-carrier-to-back-australian-vessels\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2018%2Fjul%2F21%2Fsouth-china-sea-uk-could-send-aircraft-carrier-to-back-australian-vessels&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6ufbhcgmijv%2F0DJBpEVBRbRs%3D&h=4245e524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/jul/21/south-china-sea-uk-could-send-aircraft-carrier-to-back-australian-vessels</a>"},{"pid":"3490cd9e70c1341d240ff3851f34f0ad33d74017","tid":1053455,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:47:55.000Z","msg":"事頭婆好野 事頭婆萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc393c051f7854250b145b8e38e3330fadeeb41","tid":1053455,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:57:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40698efa735ab416743adbcf436cc94ea6b2c2d4","tid":1053455,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:12:23.000Z","msg":"300萬人出來争取bno平權"},{"pid":"fcbccd9cbfa8f110f029967ebd9cb61565c459a2","tid":1053455,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}